# (use Perforce or Git LFS for large binary asset repos instead)
# *.uasset
# *.umap

# Auto-generated
FeaturePack/
Templates/

# ============================================================
# OS / editor noise
# ============================================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.suo
*.user
*.log

# JetBrains Rider
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user

# ============================================================
# Optional: uncomment to ignore content / config if desired
# ============================================================
# Content/
# Config/
